author: wddgit
body:
#### PR description:

Remove dead code not referenced or used by anything. It hasn't been under development for many years. This is motivated by the ::JetCorrector migration. This code inherits from the deprecated ::JetCorrector class. We are migrating away from that class with the intent to delete it entirely soon.

@smuzaffar This package will be basically empty after this PR is merged. I don't know how to delete a package or if it is worth the effort, but this package could be deleted entirely.

#### PR validation:

None needed. Just deletions.
title: Remove deprecated JetPartonCorrector
